Class PluginManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • at.usmile.cormorant.framework.plugin.PluginManager

  • public class PluginManager
extends java.lang.Object
    Manages the list of active plugins and caches their data. Informs other classes about plugin changes, if they implement the OnChangeListener
